- ## Configuration Examples ### ExactMatchMetric Configuration --- File: use-cases/hotpotqa/README.md --- @@ -0,0 +1,42 @@ +# HotpotQA Use Case + +This directory contains the necessary files to run prompt optimization for multi-hop question answering using the HotpotQA dataset. + +## Getting Started + +### 1. Configure Your Environment + +Make sure you have set up your API keys in the `.env` file at the root of the project: + +``` +OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_key_here +# or +HUGGINGFACE_API_KEY=your_key_here +``` + +### 3.
